{"word":"G5251 - ὑπερυψόω - hyperypsóō - hoop-er-oop-so'-o - Highly exalt","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερυψόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperypsóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-oop-so'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Highly exalt</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மேலாக உயர்த்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to exalt to the highest rank arid power, raise to supreme majesty"},{"paragraph":"2. to extol most highly"},{"paragraph":"3. to be lifted up with pride, exalted beyond measure; to carry oneself loftily"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G5312 - ὑψόω - hypsóō - hoop-so'-o/5312\">G5312</a>; to <i>elevate above</i> others, that is, <i>raise</i> to the <i>highest</i> position: - highly exalt.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5251/5251\">G5251</a>, <a href=\"#/G5310/5310\">G5310</a>, <a href=\"#/G5311/5311\">G5311</a>, <a href=\"#/G5312/5312\">G5312</a>, <a href=\"#/G5313/5313\">G5313</a>"}]}